WEBVTT

00:05.639 --> 00:09.480
Daniel Reed. Why are you looking<br>for me? We only wish to speak
with you. It's about your father.

00:09.480 --> 00:10.800
I came here to find answers.

00:10.800 --> 00:12.679
I found out my dad<br>was transferring money -

00:12.679 --> 00:14.000
to a man called Mirza Barzani.

00:14.000 --> 00:16.280
And when I found out why,<br>it made me sick.

00:16.280 --> 00:17.359
To my guts.

00:18.519 --> 00:20.640
I want to sleep in the shed.

00:20.640 --> 00:23.000
And I need you to lock me in.

00:28.239 --> 00:31.160
Hey, that's it, all right?<br>On your way. Get out!

00:32.240 --> 00:36.280
I see how you look at Alice.<br>You know she's different, don't you?

00:36.280 --> 00:41.000
I have a brain tumour.<br>You are looking at a dying man.

00:43.000 --> 00:49.074
